N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5001.26 - Notification of prize winners

State Regulations

At the conclusion of each drawing that results in the
selection of numbers, every agent shall cause the winning numbers to be posted
in a prominent place in full view at the agent's business location. In
addition, any other numbers for bonus awards or other prizes should be posted
in compliance with instructions from the commission. Notes
